CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Project object. This field set defines the project fields that are editable when project details are displayed during creation of a project, including when creating a project from an opportunity or from a template.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name of a field set used by the Project object. This field set defines the project fields that are editable when project details are displayed during creation of a project, including when creating a project from an opportunity or from a template.
CustomField.label: Project Details Editable
